/*
 *----------------------------------------------------------------------
 *
 * WmIconpositionCmd --
 *
 *	This procedure is invoked to process the "wm iconposition"
 *	Tcl command.
 *	See the user documentation for details on what it does.
 *
 * Results:
 *	A standard Tcl result.
 *
 * Side effects:
 *	See the user documentation.
 *
